post_install() {
    cat << EOF
1. Add the line:

    %network ALL=(root) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/netcfg, /usr/sbin/iwlist, /etc/rc.d/net-auto-wireless, /etc/rc.d/net-auto-wired, /usr/bin/netcfgfx

... to sudoers (with visudo)

2. Add your user to the network group (and logout to apply changes):

    $ gpasswd -a USER network

3. Launch netcfgfx prefixed with sudo:

    $ sudo netcfgfx &
EOF
}
